Version: 1.11.2
MySql usage
New version: Bungee System
Message in Config





Commands:
  /report <Spieler> <Grund> <Beweis> ----- Report a player
  /reports ----- Show all reports


  report -> (Player target, Player sender; String message; Date date - Time time;
         -> Target Name in Table + Report Counter


  reports -> Open an Inventory --> Contains: (Woolblock blue|green) Name: Reports; Hover show: sender, target message, status; Headline also sender

  Woolblock: open Inventory Headline sender ; l->r  sender Head(Name, online|offline), target Head(Name, online|offline), message(Message), status(status), go back(go back), delete(delete)


  sender Head: Inventory kill()kill, kick(kick), mesage(message), teleport(teleport), go back(goto Report by sender)

        kill: Kill the player (config)
        kick: Kick the player(config)
        message: Inventory Messages: paper(message)
                paper: send player message
        teleport:
        go back: open Inventory like Woolblock click
  target Head: see sender
  message: //// Nothing
  status: update status
  go back: go to reports inventory
  delete: delete the report (if enabled store in external Table)


